<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbe02d33f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7301"><num value="7301">§ 7301.</num><heading> Environmental impact statements</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The transfer of functions under subchapters III and IV of this chapter shall not affect the validity of any draft environmental impact statement published before <date date="1977-10-01">October 1, 1977</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbe02d340-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/91/tVII/s713">Pub. L. 95–91, title VII, § 713</ref>, <date date="1977-08-04">Aug. 4, 1977</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/91/610">91 Stat. 610</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
